headline: Mettler-Toledo Q3 Earnings Top Estimates, Sales Up Y/Y, Shares Fall
summary: MTD Q3 2024 results reflect strong growth in the Laboratory business. However, softness in the Food Retail and Industrial business reflects weaker demand.
